						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Hanumān temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1536, Ānanda, Jyēshṭha śu. 7, corresponding to 1614 A.D., June 4, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of some lands at Jānapāḍu of Taṅgeḍa-sīma by Lakshmimanēniṁgāru, son of Kṛishṇārāya and grandson of Kaṇḍalnēniṅgaru of Goṭṭimukkula.</p>						

						</summary>
